Remember to remove "localhost" from the hostfile when analyzing performance (you have to turn off graphics to do this)

To profile with gprof, add the following to your ~/.bashrc:
GMON_OUT_PREFIX="gmon".`uname -n`
export GMON_OUT_PREFIX

To use Ravel to analyze MPI traces, add the following to your ~/.bashrc:
source /share/apps/etc/uvrocks-env
